       //\xe9\xab\x98\xe5\xba\xa6100px & \xe4\xb8\x8d\xe6\x98\xbe\xe7\xa4\xba \xe2\x80\x9c\xe6\x9b\xb4\xe5\xa4\x9a\xe5\xa4\xb4\xe6\x9d\xa1\xe2\x80\x9d\xef\xbc\x9b\r\n slider($(\'.items\'));\n\n    function slider(elem) {\n        var items = elem.children(),\n                max = items.length - 1,\n                animating = false,\n                currentElem,\n                nextElem,\n                pos = 0;\n\n        sync();\n\n        return {\n            next: function () {\n                move(1);\n            },\n            prev: function () {\n                move(-1);\n            },\n            itemsNum: items && items.length\n        };\n\n        function move(dir) {\n            if (animating) {\n                return;\n            }\n            if (dir > 0 && pos == max || dir < 0 && pos == 0) {\n                if (dir > 0) {\n                    nextElem = elem.children(\'div\').first().remove();\n                    nextElem.hide();\n                    elem.append(nextElem);\n                } else {\n                    nextElem = elem.children(\'div\').last().remove();\n                    nextElem.hide();\n                    elem.prepend(nextElem);\n                }\n                pos -= dir;\n                sync();\n            }\n            animating = true;\n            items = elem.children();\n            currentElem = items[pos + dir];\n            $(currentElem).fadeIn(400, function () {\n                pos += dir;\n                animating = false;\n            });\n        }\n\n        function sync() {\n            items = elem.children();\n            for (var i = 0; i < items.length; ++i) {\n                items[i].style.display = i == pos ? \'block\' : \'\';\n            }\n        }\n\n    }\n\n    if (slideEle.itemsNum && slideEle.itemsNum > 1) {\n        setInterval(function () {\n            slideEle.next();\n        }, 4000)\n    }\n\n\n</script>\n<script>\n    function setCookie(cname, cvalue, exdays) {\n        var d = new Date();\n        d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));\n        var expires = "expires=" + d.toUTCString();\n
